Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/tdickman/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

Source: http://dudarev.com/blog/keep-vim-settings-and-plugins-in-git-repo/
